        <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/xiaoqi/ontologies/2026/3/hands-on-tools#ScreenRecording"/>
        <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI">https://github.com/webadderall/Recordly</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment>Recordly is an open-source screen recorder and editor for walkthroughs, demos, tutorials, product videos, and social clips. Record a screen or window, jump straight into the editor, and export a polished result with cursor effects, zooms, backgrounds, annotations, webcam overlays, and more.</rdfs:comment>
